We have low Vitamin D nutriture, we don't
get much sunshine, and low Vitamin D intake

00:32:07.019 --> 00:32:13.390
is highly associated with numerous issues
including depression, by the way.

00:32:13.390 --> 00:32:20.800
Once we get that taken care of the next nutrient
coming down the pike is choline.

00:32:20.800 --> 00:32:30.260
Choline is a B vitamin, it is half of the
most abundant neurotransmitter in the body,

00:32:30.260 --> 00:32:35.090
acetylcholine, responsible for every thought
and every movement that we have.

00:32:35.090 --> 00:32:36.480
[pause]

00:32:36.480 --> 00:32:42.669
In the United States ever since we started
dumping egg yolks down the drain we consume

00:32:42.669 --> 00:32:47.940
somewhere around 30 percent of our requirement
for choline.

00:32:47.940 --> 00:32:55.960
It is dramatic, there is now numerous studies
on choline, there are studies looking not

00:32:55.960 --> 00:32:59.679
only at total health but certainly at brain
function.

00:32:59.679 --> 00:33:05.910
The National Institutes of Mental Health are
supplementing people with degenerative diseases

00:33:05.910 --> 00:33:13.630
of the brain with two phospholipids found
in egg yolks: phosphatidylcholine and phosphatidylserine

00:33:13.630 --> 00:33:19.830
and have shown a slowing of the rate of progression
of Parkinson's disease and Alzheimer's disease.

00:33:19.830 --> 00:33:27.480
And studies in 18 year old boys starting college
have shown enhanced memory when they were

00:33:27.480 --> 00:33:28.480
supplemented.

00:33:28.480 --> 00:33:33.419
So we're at both ends of the spectrum with
this, it is a huge problem.

00:33:33.419 --> 00:33:43.430
If you eat just an egg yolk a day you get
about half of your choline need for the day.

00:33:43.430 --> 00:33:46.610
And then we find choline in other foods as
well.

00:33:46.610 --> 00:33:54.570
So it is very important if you are not allergic
to eggs you should be eating an egg yolk a

00:33:54.570 --> 00:33:55.570
day.

00:33:55.570 --> 00:34:00.930
An easy way is to boil 'em up at the beginning
of the week and just pop a hard boiled egg

00:34:00.930 --> 00:34:06.899
in your mouth everyday whatever you do, and
you will find that now you've got another

00:34:06.899 --> 00:34:09.810
great easy source of protein.

00:34:09.810 --> 00:34:17.109
And so add that egg to breakfast and enjoy
it because we have cut out a foundational

00:34:17.109 --> 00:34:20.020
food in our diets.

