Okay, I'm gonna say that again.

00:34:29.879 --> 00:34:35.520
Think about what you need to eat, not what
you can't eat next.

00:34:35.520 --> 00:34:41.580
Americans focus on what they can't eat; it
is so depressing [chuckles].

00:34:41.580 --> 00:34:47.700
Food is such an intimate part of our lives,
