00:34:47.700 --> 00:34:53.690
We share it with friends, we share it with
our lovers, we share it with our families,

00:34:53.690 --> 00:35:02.690
we share it at work, it is a primitive part
of our psyche to share food and break bread

00:35:02.690 --> 00:35:04.560
with another person.

00:35:04.560 --> 00:35:11.960
And so when we are more concerned when we're
at a party of fighting with the brownie on

00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:17.530
the table than we are with talking to the
cute guy or girl next to you, that's a real

00:35:17.530 --> 00:35:21.430
problem, you're missing out on life, you're
limiting your horizons.

00:35:21.430 --> 00:35:25.220
Focus on what you need to eat, not what you
can't eat next.

